content:
Salesforce is retiring Cadence Builder Classic (1.0) within the Sales Engagement product in Summer '25, replacing it with Cadence Builder 2.0. The new builder uses a simpler structure and three separate tracks to enable faster and simpler cadence building.

Beginning in Spring '25, users can only edit existing Classic cadences, and by Summer '25, they won't be able to access Cadence Builder Classic. Users should rebuild their branched cadences in Cadence Builder 2.0 before Summer '25.
title: Retirement of Cadence Builder Classic
